Detailed Description

cvmx_mio_tws::_sw_twsi_ext

This register contains an additional byte of internal address and four additional bytes of data to be used with TWSI master-mode operations.

The IA field is sent as the first byte of internal address when performing master-mode combined-read/write-with-IA operations and MIO_TWS()_SW_TWSI[EIA] is set. The D field extends the data field of MIO_TWS()_SW_TWSI for a total of 8 bytes (SOVR must be set to perform operations greater than 4 bytes).
